###  http://www.semanticweb.org/ami/ontologies/2024/0/OBC#CLO_4
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ami/ontologies/2024/0/OBC#CLO_4> rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
                                                                      <http://www.semanticweb.org/ami/ontologies/2024/0/OBC#CourseLearningOutcome> ;
                                                             <http://www.semanticweb.org/ami/ontologies/2024/0/OBC#hasContent> <http://www.semanticweb.org/ami/ontologies/2024/0/OBC#Basic_descriptive_and_inferential_statistics> ;
                                                             <http://www.semanticweb.org/ami/ontologies/2024/0/OBC#partOf> <http://www.semanticweb.org/ami/ontologies/2024/0/OBC#PLO_6_1> ;
                                                             <http://www.semanticweb.org/ami/ontologies/2024/0/OBC#action> "Able to process data" ;
                                                             <http://www.semanticweb.org/ami/ontologies/2024/0/OBC#condition> "Provided with economic and business data." ;
                                                             <http://www.semanticweb.org/ami/ontologies/2024/0/OBC#criteria> "Accurately explains phenomena reflected in data used." ;
                                                             <http://www.semanticweb.org/ami/ontologies/2024/0/OBC#description> """Mampu mengolah data ekonomi dan bisnis dengan menggunakan metode 
statistika deskriptif dan inferensial dasar termasuk pengujian hipotesis, 
serta konsep probabilitas, dan distribusi probabilitas yang relevan untuk 
menjelaskan fenomena yang tercermin dalam data yang digunakan""" ;
                                                             <http://www.semanticweb.org/ami/ontologies/2024/0/OBC#description_eng> "Able to process economic and business data using basic descriptive and inferential statistical methods, including hypothesis testing, probability concepts, and probability distributions relevant for explaining phenomena reflected in the data." ;
                                                             <http://www.semanticweb.org/ami/ontologies/2024/0/OBC#label> "CLO_4" .


