                                                             <http://www.semanticweb.org/ami/ontologies/2024/0/OBC#label> "CLO_6" .


###  http://www.semanticweb.org/ami/ontologies/2024/0/OBC#CLO_7
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ami/ontologies/2024/0/OBC#CLO_7> rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
                                                                      <http://www.semanticweb.org/ami/ontologies/2024/0/OBC#CourseLearningOutcome> ;
